Where we will use Linux OS ?
============================

1. Application deployment will happen on linux machines only.
2. Tools will be installed on Linux machines only

Ex: Docker, Jenkins, nexus, SonarQube, Elk etc......

3. Application log files will be stored in linux machines only

============
What is OS ?
============

-> Software which acts as mediator between user and computer .
-> User will communicate with computers using os .
-> without os, we can't use any computer.
-> Os provides platform to run our application in computers .
  Ex: Notepad,Calculator, browsers etc........





